
# Qattah
SwiftUI Project: Qattah is an app that help users to split their events' expenses evenly 

# Featue

Friendly UI to show the event that a user is part of
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah1.png?raw=true)
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah8.png?raw=true)
Ability to create new Event
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah2.png?raw=true)
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah3.png?raw=true)

Users can see who is part of selected event and other details such as:
 - amout they owe
 - expenses details
 - add new members
 - add new purchases
 - filter purchases by user
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah4.png?raw=true)
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah5.png?raw=true)
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah6.png?raw=true)

User can confirm if they received or pay other member
![image](https://github.com/iabdulrahman91/Qattah-IOS/blob/master/screenshot/qattah7.png?raw=true)
